</taxonomicName>
was found in the benthos of the Hron River (
<bibRefCitation author="Tirjakova" box="[1131,1307,151,176]" pageId="7" pageNumber="508" refString="Tirjakova, E. (1998) Saprobiologicke hodnotenie vod Ziarskej kotliny na zaklade druhoveho spektra a abundancie nalevnikov (Ciliophora) [Saprobiologic water evaluation of Ziarska kotlina based on the species spectrum and abundance of ciliated protozoa (Ciliophora)]. Folia faunistica Slovaca, 3, 9 - 18. [in Slovak with English title translation and summary]" type="journal article" year="1998">
Tirjaková 
<number box="[1249,1307,152,176]" pageId="7" pageNumber="508" value="1998.0">1998</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) and of the Gidra River (
<bibRefCitation author="Tirjakova" box="[298,488,188,213]" pageId="7" pageNumber="508" refString="Tirjakova, E. (2003 a) Micro- and meiozoobenthos with focus on ciliates (Ciliophora) of the Gidra River basin. Acta Zoologica Universitatis Comenianae, 45, 29 - 40." type="journal article" year="2003" yearSuffix="a">
Tirjaková 
